data.description: There is so much to love about this charming 2 story home in trendy Highland Park Estates. Every room boosts vintage charm and appeal. Featuring 4 spacious bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms with antique bathtubs, and a large open family and dining room. So many charming features including original hardwood floors, plaster dentil molding, large fireplace, and built-ins throughout the house. The huge 1/3 acre double lot is home to several mature pecan and fruit bearing citrus trees as well as a 2000 gallon Koi pond. The garage in back yard has potential to be converted into a guest house. Recent home improvements in 2018 include new roof, privacy fence and windows. Juliette balcony on second floor bedroom was fitted with a new door/storm door in 2017.
